each member of the association present and eligible to vote at the annual
                    general meeting may vote for 1 candidate for each vacant position on the
                    management committee;

for a level 2 incorporated association, or a level 3 incorporated association,
                    to which section 59 of the Act applies-appointing an auditor, an accountant or
                    an approved person for the present financial year.
